    "faq": [
      {
        "q_cn": "什么是「仁」区？",
        "a_cn": "「仁」区是一个存于场上，用于存放牌的公共区域。游戏中，可以通过某些技能效果置入或弃置「仁」区中的牌。「仁」区中的牌上限为6张；当「仁」区中的牌超过6张时，最先置入的牌将置入弃牌堆。",
        "q_en": "What is the 「Ren」 Zone?",
        "a_en": "The 「Ren」 Zone is a shared public zone on the field used to store cards. Cards can be placed into or removed from the 「Ren」 Zone through certain skill effects. The 「Ren」 Zone holds a maximum of 6 cards; when the total exceeds 6, the card placed there first is moved to the Discard Pile."
      }
    ],
    "skills": [
      "skill_deep_clarity",
      "skill_clear_the_obstruction"
    ]
  },
